sec.p:
A prediction of the target genes of lncRNAs resulted in 99 targets (Supplementary Table 2), all of which were differentially expressed genes (DEGs) (FDR < 0.05 and 
|log2FC|>1
). Their expression patterns were analyzed. Among them, 63 fitted the A pattern (Figure 4A), 28 fitted the T pattern (Figure 4B), and 8 DEGs did not fit the A and T patterns (Figures 4C,D). The 91 DEGs of A and T patterns were left for subsequent analysis.
